Class DepthFirstIterator

java.lang.Object
  cetus.hir.IRIterator
      cetus.hir.DepthFirstIterator
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.util.Iterator
public class DepthFirstIterator
extends IRIterator

Iterates over Traversable objects in depth-first order. The iteration starts from the root object that was specified in the constructor.

public void pruneOn(java.lang.Class c)
Disables traversal from an object having the specified type. For example, if traversal reaches an object with type c, it does not visit the children of the object.
